STORE - Class in com.cafebabe.core.instructions
STORE is the representation of the meta instruction that relate to the act of setting a numerical value into a local variable, this meta instruction include the following bytecode instructions {astore_0,astore_1,astore_2,astore_3, astore, dstore, dstore_0,dstore_1,dstore_2,dstore_3,fstore,fstore_0, fstore_1,fstore_2,fstore_3,istore, istore_0, istore_1, istore_2, istore_3,lstore,lstore_0,lstore_1,lstore_2,lstore_3} This representation contains information about the bytecode instruction and its context, those information are an InstructionHandle object(BCEL) that contain also information about the instruction as the name), the number of registers used by the method in which this instruction is located, the topStack value of the method at the time this instruction is executed, the number of instruction present in the method were this instruction take place, the number of the instruction in the instructions list of the instruction's method, the method name of the instruction's method, the name of the instruction's class.
STORE(InstructionHandle, short, short, int, int, int, String, String, String) - Constructor for class com.cafebabe.core.instructions.STORE
Constructor of the STORE representation
SUB - Class in com.cafebabe.core.instructions
SUB is the representation of the meta instruction that relate to the subtraction of two values, this meta instruction include the following bytecode instructions {dsub,fsub, isub, lsub} This representation contains information about the bytecode instruction and its context, those information are an InstructionHandle object(BCEL) that contain also information about the instruction as the name), the number of registers used by the method in which this instruction is located, the topStack value of the method at the time this instruction is executed, the number of instruction present in the method were this instruction take place, the number of the instruction in the instructions list of the instruction's method, the method name of the instruction's method, the name of the instruction's class.
SUB(InstructionHandle, short, short, int, int, int, String, String, String) - Constructor for class com.cafebabe.core.instructions.SUB
Constructor of the SUB representation
